<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7" id="日记">日记<a href="https://taozenanqwq.github.io/blog/24-04-25#%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0" class="hash-link" aria-label="日记的直接链接" title="日记的直接链接">​</a></h3>
